Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.58,0:02:04.12,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:121580,124124}Maya appeared in a movie for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.12,0:02:08.37,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:124124,128378}Although it was a very small role, she tried her best…
