Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.04,0:02:20.09,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:132049,140098}Maya is filled with a dream: to try many different roles, and to become an actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.05,0:02:27.56,Episode title,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:141058,147564}{\an5\pos(766,750)\fscy95\blur1\fad(500,500)}—Episode 10—\NThe New Challenge
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.45,0:02:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:158450,159534}{\i1}Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.53,0:02:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:159534,162245}{\i1}So many theaters in one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.24,0:02:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:162245,165916}{\i1}I hope I can act in a place like this one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.20,0:02:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:167209,169127}{\i1}Yeah. Why don't I go ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.08,0:02:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:170087,172214}{\i1}Asking can't hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.09,0:02:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:173090,175759}Excuse me, but the theater opens at one o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.75,0:02:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:175759,177552}Could you wait outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.55,0:03:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:177552,180722}Oh, I came to see the person in charge of this play.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.72,0:03:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:180722,183058}I mean, a manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.72,0:03:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:184726,185686}Ahh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.68,0:03:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:185686,187896}You mean Mr. Tanuma, the producer?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.89,0:03:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:187896,190273}Yes, Mr. Tanuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.27,0:03:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:190273,192317}Do you have an appointment with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.31,0:03:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:192317,194361}N-No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.36,0:03:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:194361,196154}Then you have to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.15,0:03:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:196154,198407}He's very busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.40,0:03:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:198407,199991}Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.18,0:03:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:226184,227686}Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.68,0:03:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:227686,230522}They are all real actors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.52,0:03:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:230522,232691}Oh, Mr. Tanuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.69,0:03:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:232691,233734}How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.73,0:03:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:233734,235235}Oh, that was such a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.23,0:03:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:235235,236987}Excuse me, but are you Mr. Tanuma?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.98,0:03:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:236987,239406}Yes, I'm Tanuma, but you are…?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.82,0:04:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:240824,242325}I'm Kitajima Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.32,0:04:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:242325,244828}Could you give me a role in your play?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.87,0:04:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:245871,250250}What are you talking about? Give you a role in my play when I don't even know you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.25,0:04:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:250250,252794}Just came out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.79,0:04:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:252794,255630}It's either you have some nerves or you don't know the world yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.84,0:04:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:256840,258133}{\i1}I won't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.38,0:04:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:259384,262721}It's not the same as a play in school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.72,0:04:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:262721,265197}You have to audition first, and if you get accepted…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.19,0:04:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:265197,267267}…then you have to train for about ten years.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.26,0:04:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:267267,269269}Then you can come talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.97,0:04:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:270979,275066}We are not that desperate to hire someone like you. Go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.07,0:04:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:287078,291456}I told you already about the play rights for "The Crimson Goddess".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.63,0:05:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:298632,301885}How long are you going to be like this, Miss Tsukikage?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.88,0:05:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:301885,307098}You must be having a hard time, just living each day like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.09,0:05:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:307098,311853}Your few members can't even practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.85,0:05:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:311853,315524}I doubt you can nurture an actress that can play "The Crimson Goddess".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.06,0:05:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:317067,318276}Miss Tsukikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.27,0:05:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:318276,320654}Could you please us the rights for "The Crimson Goddess"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.65,0:05:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:320654,324491}Of course we will audition from all over the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.49,0:05:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:324491,327536}I guarantee we'll make it the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.24,0:05:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:329246,331790}This is also the wish of my father…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.79,0:05:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:331790,334000}Your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.00,0:05:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:334000,338000}So he hasn't given up on "The Crimson Goddess" yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.00,0:05:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:338000,342843}If you give me the play rights,\Nthen I'll make sure…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.84,0:05:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:342843,347387}…we'll give you more than enough money so you don't have to live like this ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.38,0:05:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:347387,349057}No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.05,0:05:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:349057,351434}Even if you put up tens of thousands of dollars…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.43,0:05:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:351434,353144}…I will never give up the play rights.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.14,0:05:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:353144,354980}That's my play.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:05:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:354980,356481}My and Ozaki Ichiren's…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.40,0:06:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:359401,361401}What's wrong, Miss Tsukikage?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.40,0:06:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:361401,362362}Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.36,0:06:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:362362,365907}It's your fault!\NYou're the reason she had a stroke!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.90,0:06:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:365907,367367}Go home now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.36,0:06:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:367367,370412}We don't have time for this nonsense!\NGo get a doctor, right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.29,0:06:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:374291,376126}Doctor, this way. Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.63,0:06:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:385635,388471}Hmm? She seems to be sleeping fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.47,0:06:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:388471,389514}Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.85,0:06:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:392851,395020}Why did you—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.43,0:06:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:397438,398899}I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.89,0:06:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:398899,399941}What happened to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.32,0:06:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:411328,413288}Oh, little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.28,0:06:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:413288,415248}My name is not little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.24,0:06:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:415248,418043}My name is Kitajima Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.04,0:06:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:418043,419294}Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.25,0:07:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:425258,427218}So, have you changed your mind yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.21,0:07:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:427218,428595}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.59,0:07:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:428595,431890}About Ondine Theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.89,0:07:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:431890,433558}They will give you a full scholarship.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.55,0:07:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:433558,435977}It's a good deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.06,0:07:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:439064,441316}I like Miss Tsukikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.31,0:07:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:441316,443526}And I like my friends from Tsukikage Theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.52,0:07:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:443526,445779}Then you should join Ondine Theater even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.77,0:07:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:445779,449324}Miss Tsukikage will appreciate it\Nif she needs to feed one person less.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.32,0:07:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:449324,450282}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.83,0:07:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:455830,457707}{\i1}I hurt her again…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.20,0:07:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:459209,462462}She will hate me even more now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.46,0:07:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:462462,464130}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.13,0:07:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:464130,465006}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.46,0:07:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:468468,472472}{\i1}Miss Tsukikage will appreciate it\Nif she needs to fed one person less.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.51,0:07:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:473515,476768}{\i1}I must be a burden to Miss Tsukikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.76,0:07:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:476768,478186}{\i1}What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.18,0:08:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:478186,481481}{\i1}What can I do not to be a burden to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.06,0:08:05.94,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:482065,485944}{\fad(500,500)}Eishin Za
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.27,0:08:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:484275,488279}Performance acting is not so easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.27,0:08:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:488279,491449}Which theater are you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.44,0:08:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:491449,493493}I'm from Tsukikage Theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.49,0:08:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:493493,494202}Tsukikage?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.20,0:08:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:494202,495870}Oh, I've heard of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.87,0:08:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:495870,499791}The well-known actress, Chigusa Tsukikage…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.79,0:08:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:499791,503753}…founded it to groom an actress for "The Crimson Goddess".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.17,0:08:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:505171,506589}So, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.58,0:08:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:506589,509134}Are you the future Crimson Goddess?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.13,0:08:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:509134,514847}No, no way. Miss Tsukikage told me that there's no way I can play her right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.55,0:08:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:516558,517684}I bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.68,0:08:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:517684,521479}Famous actresses are saying\Nthat's a very tough role.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.35,0:08:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:524357,526192}Here, you should go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.69,0:08:49.32,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:526693,529320}– Good morning.\N– Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.32,0:08:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:529320,529988}Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.48,0:08:51.86,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:530488,531865}Harada Kikuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.86,0:08:55.36,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:531865,535368}A well-known actress who heads the Eishin Za.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.03,0:08:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:536036,538204}Who was that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.20,0:09:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:538204,542083}Oh, she just walked in to see if there's any role available for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.08,0:09:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:542083,545795}You know Tsukikage Theater, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.79,0:09:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:545795,547964}She's a member of that theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.96,0:09:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:547964,549424}Chigusa Tsukikage?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.42,0:09:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:549424,551092}Oh, "The Crimson Goddess"!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.09,0:09:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:551092,551885}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:551885,554095}She said that Miss Tsukikage told her…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.09,0:09:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:554095,556973}…that there's no way for her to play "The Crimson Goddess" right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.60,0:09:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:561603,563396}Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.64,0:09:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:565648,567192}Uhm, Miss Harada?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.19,0:09:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:567192,571905}She told her that there's no way for her\Nto play "The Crimson Goddess" right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.90,0:09:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:571905,574449}"Not right now".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.44,0:09:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:574449,576701}Yes, that's what she said. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.70,0:09:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:576701,577619}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.61,0:09:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:577619,579871}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.87,0:09:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:579871,583666}Then you mean she's the future Crimson Goddess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.66,0:09:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:583666,585543}Don't be silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.54,0:09:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:585543,587754}What makes you think that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.75,0:09:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:587754,590507}Miss Tsukikage is a very strict person when it comes to acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.50,0:09:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:590507,592675}Especially when it comes to "The Crimson Goddess".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.67,0:09:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:592675,595136}She didn't say that just because.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.13,0:09:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:595136,597847}If she said she can't play that now…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.84,0:10:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:597847,600934}…it might be impossible now,\Nbut it might change in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.93,0:10:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:600934,603520}In other words, she has the talent for it.{NOTE:その素質のあるということよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.52,0:10:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:603520,607398}At least that's what Miss Tsukikage believes.{NOTE:少なくとも あの月影さんはそうに混んでいるということね}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.02,0:10:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:609025,613113}Next time she comes here,\Ntell her to come see me. Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.15,0:10:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:617158,617951}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.95,0:10:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:617951,619285}Hospitalized?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.28,0:10:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:619285,620203}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.20,0:10:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:620203,623081}The doctor says it's better for her to do it immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.62,0:10:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:624624,628378}Yes. We need to examine her first,\Nbut she might need surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.37,0:10:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:628378,629587}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.58,0:10:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:629587,632799}So, how much would that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.79,0:10:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:632799,634050}Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.05,0:10:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:634050,637720}I can't say the exact amount,\Nbut at least ¥50.000.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.72,0:10:40.59,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:637720,640598}– Huh? ¥50.000?!\N– ¥50.000?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.10,0:10:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:646103,648815}¥50.000?\NThat's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.81,0:10:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:648815,651484}But we can't just leave her as she is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.94,0:10:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:652944,656030}Only if the theater was still in business, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.08,0:11:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:664080,670128}{\an8}Please bring your recyclable newspapers,\Nmagazines and old clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.12,0:11:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:670128,673923}{\an8}We'll exchange them\Nfor toilet paper and tissues.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.92,0:11:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:673923,676300}They used to be in Tsukikage Theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.76,0:11:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:685768,690607}What? You were the ones who destroyed all the costumes and equipment?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.60,0:11:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:690607,691524}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.52,0:11:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:691524,692901}We apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.31,0:11:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:694319,698656}We've been meaning to apologize ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.65,0:11:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:698656,701993}We were tricked by Onodera from Ondine Theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.99,0:11:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:701993,705580}Onodera said that he'd give us good roles at Ondine Theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.58,0:11:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:705580,707790}But we were naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.79,0:11:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:707790,710501}Later, he said he didn't remember any of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.50,0:11:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:710501,712545}We were so stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.54,0:11:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:712545,714797}You can kick or punch us all you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.79,0:11:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:714797,716299}Oh my god.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.29,0:11:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:716299,718760}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.76,0:12:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:718760,720053}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.05,0:12:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:720053,724682}It was Ondine who destroyed our theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.68,0:12:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:724682,728228}Hayami Masumi from Metropolitan Entertainment is the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.22,0:12:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:728228,729270}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.27,0:12:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:729270,730188}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.18,0:12:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:730188,734733}All he wants is the play rights for "The Crimson Goddess".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.15,0:12:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:736151,737612}How dirty they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.90,0:12:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:741908,743451}{\i1}I won't forgive them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.45,0:12:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:743451,745451}{\i1}I will never forgive them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.45,0:12:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:745451,747205}{\t(754,1754,\1c&H101010&\3c&H101010&\4c&H101010&)\i1}Never, ever!
Comment: 0,0:12:27.70,0:12:27.70,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:747704,747704}Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:12:31.50,0:12:31.50,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:751501,751501}#Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:12:34.46,0:12:34.46,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:754462,754462}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.22,0:12:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:769227,771062}Hi, little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.06,0:12:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:771062,772855}How's your teacher doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.40,0:12:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:775400,777193}What's wrong? You look pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.19,0:13:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:777193,780863}Listen to you, trying to be all nice and kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.86,0:13:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:780863,784149}We know it was you that interfered with us at the National Acting Contest…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.15,0:13:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:784150,786786}…and destroyed Tsukikage Theater!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.78,0:13:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:786786,789580}We don't need none of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.58,0:13:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:789580,790623}Go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.62,0:13:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:790623,792375}Go home…!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.37,0:13:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:792375,795837}Miss Tsukikage's condition will worsen if you come to see her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.83,0:13:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:795837,797630}You, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.63,0:13:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:797630,801550}Miss Tsukikage needs surgery, and yet…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.39,0:13:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:814397,815982}Go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.86,0:13:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:818860,820862}Mr. Masumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.86,0:13:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:820862,822322}Maya…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.32,0:13:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:822322,824073}You're from Metropolitan Entertainment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.28,0:13:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:826284,827285}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.75,0:13:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:835752,837252}Excuse me, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.42,0:14:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:838421,840006}Then she needs to be hospitalized…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.00,0:14:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:840006,843551}She needs to have surgery as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.55,0:14:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:843551,845762}But they don't have the money to pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.76,0:14:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:845762,847305}That's how it was…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.09,0:14:12.10,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:849098,852101}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.01,0:14:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:853019,855228}Hey, isn't that her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.22,0:14:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:855228,856606}Yeah, that's her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.02,0:14:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:857023,860693}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.69,0:14:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:860693,861652}Asae!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.65,0:14:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:861652,863696}That's not how you do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.69,0:14:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:863696,866324}Don't underestimate it\Njust because it's a small role.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.32,0:14:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:866324,869285}Get back a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.28,0:14:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:869285,873456}But Teacher, I want to be up in front\Nsince it's such a small role.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.49,0:14:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:874499,876000}Such a small role!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.00,0:14:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:876000,878461}What do you think a theater play is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.46,0:14:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:878461,883091}Even if it's a small role,\Nit's an important piece in the play.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.09,0:14:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:883091,884116}But listen to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.11,0:14:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:884116,887844}If you can't even play small roles, then you will never be able to play the main role!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.59,0:14:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:889597,891349}Sorry, Mr. Suzumoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.34,0:14:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:891349,893851}I know directing is your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.85,0:14:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:893851,894769}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.76,0:15:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:894769,900024}All you young people want is to be in the spotlight, without even showing any talent!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.02,0:15:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:900024,901317}Miss Harada!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.44,0:15:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:903444,904737}{\i1}Just watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.73,0:15:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:904737,906305}{\i1}Say what you want at practice…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.30,0:15:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:906305,908116}{\i1}…but once I'm on the stage, it's me who's in control.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.28,0:15:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:911285,912495}Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.12,0:15:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:914122,917791}H-Hello, how do you do?\NI'm Kitajima Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.79,0:15:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:917791,919377}How's Miss Tsukikage?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.37,0:15:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:919377,922630}I used to compete with her\Nback in my day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.63,0:15:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:922630,923423}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.42,0:15:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:923423,926884}By the way, I heard that you're going from one theater to another.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.88,0:15:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:926884,927718}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.71,0:15:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:927718,932014}I love acting and I want to become an actress someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.01,0:15:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:932014,933683}Acting is all I got.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.68,0:15:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:933683,938896}I hope I can become an actress sometime soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.72,0:15:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:939729,940814}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.48,0:15:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:944485,948322}Display joy, anger, sadness and happiness using this chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.32,0:15:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:948322,949282}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.28,0:15:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:949282,950699}You can use any words.\NHere, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.58,0:15:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:955580,957540}{\i1}Using the chair…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.54,0:15:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:957540,958499}{\i1}What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.49,0:16:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:958499,960877}{\i1}I've never done this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.87,0:16:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:960877,964714}{\i1}Joy, anger, sadness and happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.71,0:16:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:964714,967175}{\i1}What should I do using this chair?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.13,0:16:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:969135,970595}Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.59,0:16:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:970595,972430}You bought me a new chair!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.43,0:16:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:972430,973306}Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.30,0:16:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:973306,975808}Thank you, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.80,0:16:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:975808,977643}I wanted a new chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.27,0:16:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:979270,982690}Oh, look!\NThere's a scratch on the back, how bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.69,0:16:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:982690,985193}Why am I so unlucky…?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.69,0:16:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:985693,986652}Well!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.65,0:16:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:986652,989405}I can go exchange it for a better one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.40,0:16:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:989405,989989}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.98,0:16:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:989989,991906}Good, you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.53,0:16:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:997538,999540}Sit on this chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.45,0:16:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1000458,1002543}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.54,0:16:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1002543,1004962}Miss Harada is putting her to the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.75,0:16:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1005755,1006964}Here, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.96,0:16:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1010968,1013179}{\i1}Sit on the tipped chair…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.17,0:16:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1013179,1014388}{\i1}Sit on the tipped chair…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.39,0:17:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1024398,1025483}What is she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.48,0:17:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1025483,1028611}She said to sit on the chair,\Nbut she's on the floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.94,0:17:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1029946,1031948}Why did you take that pose?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.94,0:17:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1031948,1038538}W-Well, the chair is tipped, so if I was sitting on this chair, then I would be tipped, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.12,0:17:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1043125,1043917}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.91,0:17:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1043917,1047880}The pose goes best with the tipped chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.88,0:17:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1047880,1052176}I'm getting what you meant now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.17,0:17:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1052176,1053928}Candidate for "The Crimson Goddess".\NI see it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.92,0:17:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1053928,1055555}Theater is a serious deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.55,0:17:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1055555,1058015}You never know what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.01,0:17:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1058015,1060434}This was to test her theater spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.06,0:17:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1062061,1064230}And, how did she do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.31,0:17:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1067316,1068818}{\i1}Tremendous!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.23,0:17:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1070236,1072280}Everyone, be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.70,0:17:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1075700,1077702}I have an announcement to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.12,0:18:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1080121,1083374}We will no longer keep Yuki Asae as the baby sitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.37,0:18:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1083374,1084625}Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.50,0:18:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1087503,1091173}Instead, we'll go with Kitajima Maya!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.05,0:18:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1093050,1095219}This girl here\Nwill play the baby sitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.63,0:18:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1098639,1100850}Are you serious, Miss Harada?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.85,0:18:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1100850,1104562}It's five days before our first play\Nand you're switching roles like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.56,0:18:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1104562,1108774}He's right. And she just walked in right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.77,0:18:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1108774,1110484}Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.48,0:18:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1110484,1112069}The decision has been made.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.44,0:18:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1114447,1115698}Asae!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.69,0:18:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1115698,1117617}Miss Harada.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.61,0:18:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1117617,1121329}She should learn from this lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.32,0:18:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1121329,1124707}That conceited, big headed girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.33,0:18:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1125333,1128628}So, you are giving me a role?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.62,0:18:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1128628,1129544}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.54,0:18:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1129544,1130963}Isn't that what you wanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.96,0:18:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1130963,1133549}Here's the script.\NTry your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.54,0:18:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1133549,1135301}But what about that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.30,0:18:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1135301,1136969}Don't mind her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.96,0:18:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1136969,1139639}All you need to do is try your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.63,0:19:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1139639,1144268}If you make mistakes,\Nwe'll fire you too, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.26,0:19:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1144268,1145226}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.02,0:19:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1149023,1151359}I can act again now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.35,0:19:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1151359,1152985}I can be on stage again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.02,0:19:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1154028,1157657}{\i1}Miss Tsukikage,\Nthe door is opening up for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.62,0:19:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1162620,1163663}Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.41,0:19:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1167416,1168542}Teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.54,0:19:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1168542,1169877}Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.12,0:19:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1171128,1171796}Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.79,0:19:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1171796,1173798}Where's Teacher?\NWhere is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.79,0:19:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1173798,1175341}Don't worry about Miss Tsukikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.67,0:19:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1178678,1181389}Rei, what happened to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.38,0:19:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1181389,1183933}She was admitted\Nto the University Medical Center.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.93,0:19:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1183933,1184725}So, she's in the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.72,0:19:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1184725,1185518}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.51,0:19:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1185518,1187978}I just came back from taking her there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.97,0:19:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1187978,1189438}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.43,0:19:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1189438,1190981}But what about all the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.98,0:19:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1190981,1193901}Well, they say we don't have to worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.90,0:19:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1193901,1199240}Someone has paid for it all. He even chartered us a car to go to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.24,0:20:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1199240,1200574}Someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.57,0:20:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1200574,1202993}He sent a gift, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.99,0:20:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1202993,1204912}What do you think it is, Maya?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.91,0:20:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1204912,1205413}A gift?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.41,0:20:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1205413,1207331}Here, close your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.33,0:20:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1207331,1208581}Okay…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.54,0:20:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1210543,1211793}You can open them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.09,0:20:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1222096,1223389}Oh, that's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.38,0:20:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1223389,1224849}Mr. Purple Rose!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.84,0:20:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1224849,1227977}Yes. It's your secret admirer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.97,0:20:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1227977,1229895}Here. He sent a fan letter with it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.06,0:20:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1235067,1240573}{\i1}"I finally found out where you live, and then learned that Miss Tsukikage is very ill."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.57,0:20:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1240573,1245077}{\i1}"I don't want to be meddlesome,\Nbut please accept my good intentions."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.07,0:20:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1245077,1249248}{\i1}"I'm waiting for the day\NI can see you on the stage again."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.58,0:20:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1253586,1255129}{\i1}Waiting…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.92,0:21:39.84,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1297922,1299840}Eishin Za
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.28,0:22:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1326283,1328994}{\i1}Please watch me, Mr. Purple Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.03,0:22:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1331038,1332957}{\i1}You'll get your share, girl.
Comment: 0,0:22:50.36,0:22:50.36,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:1370369,1370369}Ending
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.62,0:23:03.75,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1377627,1383757}{\blur3}It is lonely by myself…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.75,0:23:09.84,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1383757,1389847}{\blur3}…and I almost stumble.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.84,0:23:21.85,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1389847,1401857}{\blur3}Somewhere calls me here,\Njust like a whisper in the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.85,0:23:33.99,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1401857,1413997}{\blur3}Purple light, shining down\Non the horizon…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.99,0:23:39.87,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1413997,1419877}{\blur3}…more surer than words…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.87,0:23:46.00,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1419877,1426007}{\blur3}…telling us gently…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.00,0:23:52.09,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1426007,1432097}{\blur3}…that we'll meet\Neach other someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.09,0:23:58.18,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1432097,1438187}{\blur3}Of course you can\Nfly from far away…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.18,0:24:04.19,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1438187,1444197}{\blur3}…for the dream\Non my cheek…
